<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚7點開始就是煙火大會啦！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我從現在開始<delay8 />就已經在期待晚上的活動了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算要辦到晚上12點，我也完全不介意喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="33" />上能夠
舉辦這種華麗的活動，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的是很有一套呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />做好覺悟了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還問我什麼覺悟？<delay20 />
當然是今天的煙火大會啊！
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要看著不斷射向空中的煙火，<delay8 />
討厭的事都能忘得一乾二淨喔？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay20 />能不能快點到晚上啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到你的臉，讓我想起來了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚有煙火大會啊。<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你打算怎麼辦呢？
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和大家一起看似乎很不錯，<delay8 />
但在家裡悠哉地欣賞好像也不賴<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真令人煩惱呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">話說<tag a="110" b="3" />……
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你會覺得緊張嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等等煙火大會就要開始了喔。
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是不會為了這種事感到緊張啦！<delay frames="40" />
因為在祭典前，<delay8 /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經有
給自己加油打氣過啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好咧！<delay20 />再過不久<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是煙火大會啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經開始期待<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這次會發射什麼樣的煙火啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說還好今天是晴天呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟這可是難得的煙火大會，<delay8 />
當然會希望煙火能漂亮地綻放啊。
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />灌注心力，<delay8 />並使其盛大地綻放，<delay8 />
這跟照顧花朵的道理是一樣的。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這些都會讓人投入感情喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀～<delay20 />雖然煙火大會已經結束了，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是在我的心中，<delay8 />煙火依舊
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不斷地朝空中發射呢！
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay20 />我實在太過興奮了，<delay8 />
感覺就這樣睡覺有些可惜呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />祭典剛結束時的那種氣氛，<delay8 />
我還挺喜歡的喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我現在也不想一個人獨處，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以能跟<tag a="110" b="3" />說上話
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的太好啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火結束後<delay8 />
就會突然變得很安靜呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我比較喜歡熱鬧的氣氛，<delay8 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喜歡到希望每天都能
舉辦煙火大會喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火大會真的超開心的！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的煙火也到此告一段落<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />令人難免有些失落呢。
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />明年也能跟死黨一起
在這座島上看煙火，一想到這……<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就一點也不會感到寂寞喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說<delay8 />今年的煙火
真的非常漂亮啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最近一個月，<delay8 />每週日都是煙火大會，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />害我現在一時間想不到<delay8 />
該怎麼度過下週日的夜晚呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年最後的煙火<delay8 />
也被盛大地射向空中咧！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的腦海中還殘留著煙火的聲響……<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚可能會興奮得睡不著，
就這樣醒著到早上呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>